# 统一文本文件换行符为 LF（避免 Windows/Mac/Linux 协作时 CRLF 战争）
# Git 提交时统一存为 LF；checkout 时按各操作系统自动转换
* text=auto eol=lf

# 二进制文件不做换行符处理
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.svg binary
*.glb binary
*.gltf binary
*.mp4 binary
*.webm binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
